Dialogue: 0,00:03:58.860,00:04:04.860,辉英,,0,0,0,,In multiple dimensions, you need to take more than two cells to reconstruct a gradient.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:04.860,00:04:13.860,辉英,,0,0,0,,Usually you take multiple cells around you and perform a least squares type of estimate for the gradient value.
